/bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093424/2022-abus-smiley-3-youth-kids-bicycle-helmet-01-768x576.jpg 768w\"></a></p><p>For kids, the new Smiley 3.0 brings updated designs and colors and the option for a USB-rechargeable clip-on rear light. Some models will come with it, but it can be added afterward for those that don’t.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093257/2022-abus-colors-and-models-bicycle-helmet-01.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093257/2022-abus-colors-and-models-bicycle-helmet-01.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1175\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093257/2022-abus-colors-and-models-bicycle-helmet-01.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093257/2022-abus-colors-and-models-bicycle-helmet-01-297x218.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093257/2022-abus-colors-and-models-bicycle-helmet-01-800x588.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093257/2022-abus-colors-and-models-bicycle-helmet-01-120x88.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093257/2022-abus-colors-and-models-bicycle-helmet-01-768x564.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093257/2022-abus-colors-and-models-bicycle-helmet-01-1536x1128.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093257/2022-abus-colors-and-models-bicycle-helmet-01.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093257/2022-abus-colors-and-models-bicycle-helmet-01.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093257/2022-abus-colors-and-models-bicycle-helmet-01-297x218.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093257/2022-abus-colors-and-models-bicycle-helmet-01-800x588.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093257/2022-abus-colors-and-models-bicycle-helmet-01-120x88.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093257/2022-abus-colors-and-models-bicycle-helmet-01-768x564.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093257/2022-abus-colors-and-models-bicycle-helmet-01-1536x1128.jpg 1536w\"></a></p><p>Across the line, look for plenty of color options and, for kids, a ton of graphics to appeal to anyone. Pretty much all of the new helmets will start shipping in Spring 2022, pricing TBA. In the meantime, check out Abus’ current lineup at <a href=\"https://mobil.abus.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">mobil.abus.com</a>.</p><h3>Sena R2 X chats directly with Amazon Alexa</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093429/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-01.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093429/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-01.jpg\" alt=\"sena r2 road bike helmet with intercom wireless communication and bluetooth speaker\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1200\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093429/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-01.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093429/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-01-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093429/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-01-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093429/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-01-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093429/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-01-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093429/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-01-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093429/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-01.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093429/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-01.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093429/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-01-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093429/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-01-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093429/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-01-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093429/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-01-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093429/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-01-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\"></a></p><p>Coming for 2022 is an updated version of <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/03/20/sena-r1-evo-smart-helmet-integrates-voice-commands-lights-radio-more/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">their R1 road helmet</a> that gets a more aerodynamic, sporty design. The 2022 <a href=\"http://www.sena.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Sena</a> R2 will come in three versions…the standard R2 with Bluetooth Intercom that connects up to 4 riders, the R2 EVO with their proprietary Mesh Network communication, and an R2 X that can also interact with Amazon Alexa directly from the helmet.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093435/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-02.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093435/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-02.jpg\" alt=\"sena r2 road bike helmet with intercom wireless communication and bluetooth speaker shown from behind\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1200\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093435/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-02.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093435/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-02-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093435/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-02-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093435/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-02-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093435/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-02-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093435/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-02-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093435/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-02.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093435/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-02.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093435/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-02-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093435/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-02-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093435/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-02-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093435/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-02-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093435/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-02-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\"></a></p><p>If you’re unfamiliar with Sena, their Mesh Intercom Technology allows you to link with and communicate with an unlimited number of other riders. It’s great for big groups when you need to keep everyone together, and it comes from years of development on the moto side of their business.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093442/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-04.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093442/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-04.jpg\" alt=\"control buttons for sena r2 road bike helmet with intercom wireless communication\" width=\"1620\" height=\"600\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093442/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-04.jpg 1620w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093442/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-04-297x110.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093442/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-04-800x296.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093442/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-04-120x44.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093442/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-04-768x284.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093442/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-04-1536x569.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1620px) 100vw, 1620px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb28 src ng ngcb28 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093442/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-04.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093442/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-04.jpg 1620w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093442/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-04-297x110.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093442/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-04-800x296.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093442/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-04-120x44.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093442/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-04-768x284.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/13093442/sena-r2-road-bike-helmet-with-walkie-talkie-04-1536x569.jpg 1536w\"></a></p><p>Full details on the Amazon Alexa integration will be released later, but we imagine it’s a good way to play music, check the weather, or just get an answer to all those weird little questions you think of when you’re out riding…all hands free.</p><p>Want to add their Bluetooth intercom system to your existing helmet? Check out the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/05/07/sena-pi-adds-universal-2-way-wireless-communication-to-any-helmet/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Sena Pi universal headset kit</a> that clips to almost any helmet’s straps and gives you quick, easy communication between two riders.</p></section></article></div></div>","author":"Tyler Benedict","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"806342a5f3dbbfc385975efa5f27aa2c15fa632f94dc2a22cd6c3ee124d8d490","category":"Cycling"}